Armed bandits are currently attacking two villages in Faskari Local Government Area of Katsina State, SaharaReporters has gathered. The villages under attack are Bilbis and Hayin Gadar Daudawa. No fewer than 20 people have been reportedly killed by bandits in Faskasi Local Government Area in the last two weeks. Sahara Reporters Media “They are presently shooting sporadically and stealing our cows, burning our houses, please help us alert the security agencies,” a resident of Bilbis told SaharaReporters. 



